  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393820/extras/62bbae8adb8cdb60596c3e119ffac072.poster.avif?t=1774025402\" width=600 height=550 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393820/extras/62bbae8adb8cdb60596c3e119ffac072.webm?t=1774025402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>ENCOUNTER</strong></i></u><i><strong> </strong></i>dangerous monsters as you explore caves, castles, and crypts on journeying through your childhood home of Vann’s Point and beyond the world of Lyrian! <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393820/extras/03d6edf808cca6e1c9b977afb145456c.avif?t=1774025402\" width=595 height=236 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>OVERCOME</strong></i></u><i><strong> </strong></i>any challenge that stands between you and redemption on your return to a now unfamiliar childhood home. Face the sins of your past and reunite with friends from years past. Even ignite new relationships as you right the wrongs that haunt you! <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393820/extras/c4dec20690342e60ae27546d2038e9a3.avif?t=1774025402\" width=595 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>DISCOVER</strong></i></u><i><strong> </strong></i>mysterious secrets of those who came before as you collect fragments of long forgotten knowledge. Learn of dangerous prophecies and legends foretelling what is yet to come! <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393820/extras/7bcd78e8048304a2411bbf8e845d59d1.avif?t=1774025402\" width=595 height=283 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Countless ways to play: Chaos, Altars, Curses and more</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A nostalgic hybrid chiptune/organic OST</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fun, story-building side quests</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More than a dozen dungeons </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Extensive post-game content</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 24 hours of gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 pursuable relationships</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 20 bosses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plenty more!</p></li></ul>",
